<div class="wide-dark-box">
    <div>
        <h1>About S.H.I.F.T</h1>
        <p>
            Welcome to the <strong>System for Healthcare Integration and Facility Tracking (S.H.I.F.T)</strong> – a cutting-edge solution designed to modernize and streamline hospital ward operations. Developed with the goal of improving efficiency, accuracy, and patient care, S.H.I.F.T replaces traditional, paper-based systems with a digital, user-friendly platform tailored for small community hospitals.
        </p>
        <p>
            <strong>S.H.I.F.T</strong> enables healthcare staff to efficiently manage daily ward activities, including patient admissions, discharges, medical treatments, doctor visits, and resource allocation. By providing a centralized and accessible platform, S.H.I.F.T ensures that hospital staff can focus more on patient care and less on administrative tasks, ultimately enhancing the quality of healthcare services.
        </p>

        <h2>Key Features of S.H.I.F.T</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Patient Management:</strong> Seamlessly handle patient admissions, movement, and discharges, while keeping accurate and up-to-date records.</li>
            <li><strong>Patient Care:</strong> Record vital signs, manage medication administration, and ensure effective communication between nurses and doctors.</li>
            <li><strong>Doctor-Patient Interaction:</strong> Facilitate easy access to patient records, track patient progress, and enable doctors to prescribe treatments and medications with ease.</li>
            <li><strong>Consumables & Script Management:</strong> Efficiently manage hospital consumables and medications, ensuring wards are well-stocked and prescriptions are promptly processed.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>
            The System for Healthcare Integration and Facility Tracking was developed to make healthcare technology more accessible and patient-centric. By focusing on improving the day-to-day operations of hospital wards, our goal is to empower healthcare professionals to deliver better, more coordinated care. With S.H.I.F.T, we’re helping hospitals embrace a more efficient, data-driven approach to ward management.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>